  "texts": [
    "This necessitates that researchers know why and how the model creates certain chemicals.",
    "There must be a high degree of data robustness in GAI models.",
    "This is because the training data for these models is often imperfect and contains noise.",
    "Despite these limitations, GAI models are promising to revolutionize drug discovery.",
    "These models can potentially speed up and lower the overall cost of drug development by automating the generation of novel compounds."
